\c 18
\s Imivuzo yobupristi
\p
\v 1 Abapristi, amaLevi, isizwe sonke sakoLevi, kasiyikuba lesabelo lelifa kanye loIsrayeli\x + Nani 18.20. Nani 26.62.\x*; bazakudla iminikelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyenziwe ngomlilo, lelifa layo\x + Nani 18.8,9. 1 Kor. 9.13.\x*.
\v 2 Ngakho kabayikuba lelifa phakathi kwabafowabo; iN\nd kosi\nd* iyilifa labo, njengokukhuluma kwayo kibo.
\p
\v 3 Lalokhu kuzakuba lilungelo labapristi elivela ebantwini, kulabo abahlaba umhlatshelo, loba inkabi loba imvu; njalo bazanika umpristi umkhono lemihlathi yomibili lolusu\x + Levi 7.30-34.\x*.
\v 4 Okokuqala kwamabele akho, yewayini lakho elitsha, leyamafutha akho, lengqabutho yoboya bezimvu zakho, uzamupha yona\x + Eks. 22.29. Nani 18.12.\x*.
\v 5 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho imkhethile kuzo zonke izizwe zakho, ukuthi eme akhonze ebizweni leN\nd kosi\nd*, yena lamadodana akhe, zonke izinsuku\x + 17.12.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Uba-ke umLevi esiza evela loba kukuliphi lamasango akho kuIsrayeli wonke lapho ahlala khona njengowezizwe, eze\x + Nani 35.2,3.\x* ngesifiso sonke somphefumulo wakhe\x + 12.15.\x* endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* ezayikhetha\x + 12.5.\x*,
\v 7 khona ezakhonza ebizweni leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe\x + 17.12.\x* njengabo bonke abafowabo amaLevi\x + 1 Lan. 23.6. 2 Lan. 31.2.\x*, emiyo khona phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 17.12.\x*.
\v 8 Azakudla izabelo ezilinganayo, ngaphandle kwezinto zakhe ezathengiswayo zaboyise\x + 2 Lan. 31.4. Neh. 12.44,47. 13.10.\x*.
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli baxwayiswa ukuthi bangavumisi
\p
\v 9 Lapho usufikile elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona, ungafundi ukwenza ngokwezinengiso zalezozizwe\x + Levi 18.26-30. 12.29-31.\x*.
\v 10 Kakuyikutholakala phakathi kwakho owenza indodana yakhe lendodakazi yakhe idabule emlilweni\x + Levi 18.21.\x*, owenza ukuvumisa\x + 18.14. Nani 22.7. 23.23. Josh. 13.22; 1 Sam. 15.23; 28.8. 2 Kho. 17.17.\x*, ochasisa ngemibono\x + 18.14. Mika 5.12; Isa. 2.6; Levi 19.26.\x*, lowenza imilingo\x + Levi 19.26. Nani 24.1.\x*, lomthakathi\x + Eks. 7.11. Isa. 47.9.\x*,
\v 11 lophosayo\x + Hlab. 58.5. Isa. 47.9.\x*, lolamadlozi\x + Levi 20.27. Levi 19.31.\x*, lolumbayo\x + Levi 20.27. Levi 19.31.\x*, lobuza kwabafileyo\x + 1 Sam. 28.7.\x*.
\v 12 Ngoba wonke owenza lezizinto uyisinengiso eN\nd kosi\nd*ni. Langenxa yalezizinengiso iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho iyabaxotsha elifeni phambi kwakho\x + Levi 18.24,25. Dute. 9.4.\x*.
\v 13 Uzakuba ngopheleleyo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho.
\v 14 Ngoba izizwe lezi, ozakudla ilifa lazo, zalalela abachasisa ngemibono\x + 18.14. Mika 5.12; Isa. 2.6; Levi 19.26.\x* labavumisi\x + 18.14. Nani 22.7. 23.23. Josh. 13.22; 1 Sam. 15.23; 28.8. 2 Kho. 17.17.\x*; kodwa wena, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho kayikuvumelanga okunjalo.
\s UNkulunkulu uthembisa ukuvusela abantu umprofethi
\p
\v 15 IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakuvusela uMprofethi ophuma phakathi kwakho kubafowenu onjengami; yena limlalele\x + 18.18. Joha. 1.21,25,45. Seb. 3.22. 7.37.\x*.
\v 16 Njengakho konke owakucelayo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho eHorebe ngosuku lokuhlangana\x + 9.10.\x*, usithi: Kangingaphindi ngilizwe ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wami, ngingabe ngisawubona lumlilo omkhulu, ukuze ngingafi\x + Eks. 20.19.\x*.
\v 17 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Benze kuhle kwabakukhulumileyo\x + 5.28.\x*.
\v 18 Ngizabavusela uMprofethi ophuma phakathi kwabafowabo onjengawe\x + 18.15.\x*; ngizabeka amazwi ami emlonyeni wakhe\x + Jer. 1.9. 5.14. Joha. 17.8.\x*, njalo akhulume kibo konke engizamlaya khona\x + Joha. 4.25. Joha. 8.28. 12.49,50.\x*.
\v 19 Kuzakuthi-ke loba ngubani ongayikulalela amazwi ami azawakhuluma ebizweni lami, ngizakubuza kuye\x + Seb. 3.23.\x*.
\v 20 Kodwa umprofethi oziqhenya\x + 17.12.\x* ekhuluma ilizwi ebizweni lami engingamlayanga ukulikhuluma\x + 13.5. Jer. 14.14,15. Zek. 13. 3.\x*, loba ekhuluma ebizweni labanye onkulunkulu, lowomprofethi uzakufa\x + Jer. 2.8.\x*.
\v 21 Njalo uba usithi enhliziyweni yakho: Sizakwazi njani ilizwi iN\nd kosi\nd* engalikhulumanga?
\v 22 Lapho umprofethi ekhuluma ebizweni leN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Jer. 28.9; Dute. 13.1-3.\x*, uba leyonto ingenzeki kumbe ingafiki, lelo yilizwi iN\nd kosi\nd* engalikhulumanga; umprofethi ulikhulume ngokuziqhenya; ungamesabi\x + 18.20.\x*.